    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "hl_sub",
      "x": 60,
      "y": 104,
      "width": 1000,
      "height": 44,
      "text": "Each product is a column; each platform it leans on is drawn once, as a band.\nRead down a column for what a project depends on, across a band for who shares the platform.",
